name: Rewind! – Yellow Tee
description: This tee has a discharge print for a softer, less plasticky handle. The graphic is only printed on the front body panel and disappears into the seams – a much harder and more expensive process to achieve, and as with all I am Colin tees, it features a tonal 2.5cm embroidery of the pants & crossbones logo on the left sleeve. Each t-shirt is lovingly made from 100% cotton to the custom IAC cut and fit and double enzyme washed for a luxuriously soft handle to the garment.
